  <scopecontent id="aspace_83e1c69e14343b2b82d35efc68ed122a">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Projects, articles, maps, audiotapes, reports, and other materials pertaining to Ewald's career as a planner. Included are projects in Arkansas and the Ozarks, and material concerning the Appalachian Institute, Santa Barbara's Alternative Comprehensive Community Environmental Study System, the American Institute of Planners, and environmentalism.</p>  </scopecontent>
